            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-881721428" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-881721428" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="881721428">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/wzcjojo/">魏知超</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar20 rating" title="较差"></span>
                    <span>2016-07-28</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">弃！标题和介绍严重误导读者。原书出版于1942年，论述的是老派戏剧哲学。古板老旧也就罢了，关键是贯穿始终的其实是戏剧哲学，而不是写作技巧和写作原则。如果你是冲着写作指南买来看，一定觉得上当。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1089963050">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1089963050" class="vote-count">1</span>
